###  https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/block02
:block02 rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                  <https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/ToyBlock> ;
         <https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/hasAffordance> :graspingAffordance ;
